column4: Dec. 10 – Cambodian gold medalist of Asian Games 2018 Saly Ou Moeut has won King Cup-Jet Ski World Cup 2018 in Pattaya
column6: according to Watercraft Federation of Cambodia.------The same source said on Sunday that Saly won the King’s Cup in Ski Modified game by scoring the first in four consecutive rounds.------As a custom of this grand tournament
column7: the names of the champions will be engraved on the trophy so that the history will remember him forever.------
